(5, 'LG - 55\" Class- OLED - Curved - 2160p - Smart - 3D - 4K Ultra HD TV', 4, 840661295, '2999.99', '0.00', 9, 11, 0, '<p><span>This TV\'s curved screen produces an enhanced sense of depth and immersion, and the 4K resolution displays movies, TV shows and more with 4x the resolution of Full HD. Plus, OLED technology delivers lifelike colors, crisp images and infinite contrast for outstanding picture quality.</span></p>', '<p><strong>54-5/8\" screen (measured diagonally from corner to corner)</strong></p><p>A great size for a living room or mid-sized home theater space. The curved screen\'s dramatically improved field of view creates a panoramic effect and helps the picture feel larger.</p><p><strong>OLED TVs perform well in all lighting condition</strong>s</p><p>They offer a high degree of color accuracy, wide viewing angles and a picture that is virtually blur free.</p><p><strong>2160p resolution for breathtaking HD images</strong></p><p>Watch 4K movies and TV shows at 4x the resolution of Full HD, and upscale your current HD content to gorgeous, Ultra HD-level picture quality.*</p><p><strong>Brilliant contrast and rich color</strong></p><p>Infinite contrast ratio produces a deep, rich black during dark scenes for great contrast. 4-color pixel technology delivers bright whites for a wide, high-contrast color spectrum.</p><p><strong>With webOS 2.0, Smart TV delivers a huge world of entertainment</strong></p><p>Stream movies, videos, music and more, and use the included Web browser to surf your favorite websites. Built-in Wi-Fi connects to a wireless home network.</p><p><strong>Rapid Web browsing and downloading</strong></p><p>Multitask, browse the Web, and download apps faster with a quad-core processor.</p><p><strong>Flicker-free 3D</strong></p><p>Bring the movie theater thrills of 3D into your home. 2 pairs of 3D glasses are included. Additional pairs sold separately.</p><p><strong>Magic Remote with scroll wheel and Voice Search</strong></p><p>Simply click, point