(10, 'Dell - XPS Desktop - Intel Core i7', 23, 984877951, '839.99', '899.99', 12, 7, 1, '<p><span>Get a powerful mini tower with the Dell XPS 8900 desktop computer. With its ultra-fast Intel i7 processor, plenty of RAM and discrete graphics card, this computer is designed to handle even the most demanding workflows. Paired with the Windows 10 operating system, the Dell XPS 8900 mini desktop gets the job done.</span></p>', '<p><strong>Windows 10 operating system</strong></p><p>Windows 10 brings back the popular Start Menu from Windows 7 and introduces new features, like the Edge Web browser that lets you markup Web pages on your screen.<a href=\"http://www.bestbuy.com/Windows10\">Learn more</a></p><p><strong>6th Gen Intel¿ Core I7-6700 processor</strong></p><p>Powerful quad-core processing performance. Intel Turbo Boost Technology delivers dynamic extra power when you need it, while increasing energy efficiency when you don\'t.</p><p><strong>16GB system memory for intense multitasking and gaming</strong></p><p>Reams of high-bandwidth DDR4 RAM to smoothly run your graphics-heavy PC games and video-editing applications, as well as numerous programs and browser tabs all at once.</p><p><strong>DVD/CD burner</strong></p><p>Reads and writes to a variety of media formats, including DVD+R/RW, DVD-R/RW and CD-R/RW.</p><p><strong>1TB hard drive for immense file storage space</strong></p><p>Holds your extensive collection of digital photos, music, HD videos and DVD-quality movies.</p><p><strong>NVIDIA GeForce GT 730 graphics</strong></p><p>Driven by 2GB DDR3 dedicated video memory to quickly render high-quality images for videos and games.</p><p><strong>Built-in media reader for simple photo transfer</strong></p><p>Supports CompactFlash Card type I, CompactFlash Card type II, Memory Stick, Memory Stick PRO, MultiMediaCard, SD, SmartMedia Card, Memory Stick Duo, xD-Picture Card, Memory Stick PRO Duo, min...</p><p><strong>6 USB 3.0 ports maximizes the latest high-speed devices</s