(22, 'Samsung - Galaxy S7 32GB - Gold Platinum', 61, 488782708, '649.99', '0.00', 18, 16, 1, '<p><span>Combine incredible water resistance with a great screen and a powerful processor, and you get the Samsung Galaxy S7. It\'s built to withstand dunks in water for up to 30 minutes, and then you can wipe it off and get playing with a 5.1-inch touchscreen. The Samsung Galaxy S7 enjoys a quad-core processor for ultra-fast responsiveness.</span></p>', '<ul><li>Qualcomm Snapdragon 820 processor</li><li>Quad-core 2.2GHz processor and 4GB of RAM deliver outstanding overall performance for opening and running applications, flipping through menus, running home screens and more.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Android 6.0 Marshmallow OS</strong></li><li>SMore to Love.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>4G LTE speed</strong></li><li>Provides fast Web connection for downloading apps, streaming content and staying connected with social media.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>5.1\" Super AMOLED HD touch screen</strong></li><li>Extra-large screen is matched with a slim body to comfortably fit in your hand. Offers 16:9 cinema-like screen ratio that\'s perfect for viewing of videos, photos and games.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>12.0MP rear-facing camera for full HD pictures and videos</strong></li><li>The worlds first dual pixel smartphone camera makes capturing low light photos a breeze. Also includes a front-facing 5.0MP camera for self-portraits and video.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>32GB internal memory plus microSD slot</strong></li><li>Provides plenty of storage space for your contacts, music, apps and more. Expand storage up to 200GB by adding a microSD card (sold separately).</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Cloud support lets you access your files anywhere</strong></li><li>Store your photos, videos, documents and other files on Drive for secure access across multiple devices. Fees may apply.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Use your smartphone as a mobile hotspot</strong></li><li>Share your 4G data connection with other compatible wireless devices.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Always on Display</strong></li><li>Get the time or notifications without waking your screen.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Water-resistant IP68</strong></li><li>Repels spills, splashes, and even dunks so you wont be putting all your hopes in a pathetic bowl of rice. Water-resistant in up to 5 feet of water for up to 30 minutes.</li><li><br></li></ul><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 00:34:24', '2016-04-27 00:34:24'),
(23, 'Samsung - Galaxy S7 edge 32GB - Silver Titanium', 44, 963706270, '799.99', '0.00', 18, 16, 0, '<p><span>Work, rest and play with the Samsung Galaxy S7 edge. A massive 5.5-inch Super AMOLED touchscreen goes all the way to the edges of the phone so that you get the maximum area possible to work with. Solid water resistance, great processing and masses of memory round out this Samsung Galaxy S7 edge.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>Qualcomm Snapdragon 820 processor</strong></li><li>Quad-core 2.2GHz processor and 4GB of RAM deliver outstanding overall performance for opening and running applications, flipping through menus, running home screens and more.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Android 6.0 Marshmallow OS</strong></li><li>SMore to Love.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>4G LTE speed (Available in select markets)</strong></li><li>Provides fast Web connection for downloading apps, streaming content and staying connected with social media.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>5.5\" Super AMOLED Quad HD touch screen</strong></li><li>Extra-large screen is matched with a slim body to comfortably fit in your hand. Offers 16:9 cinema-like screen ratio that\'s perfect for viewing of videos, photos and games.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Dual Edge Design and Experience</strong></li><li>Get real-time scores and news delivered right to your edge.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>12.0MP rear-facing camera for full HD pictures and videos</strong></li><li>The worlds first dual pixel smartphone camera makes capturing low light photos a breeze. Also includes a front-facing 5.0MP camera for self-portraits and video.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>32GB internal memory plus microSD slot</strong></li><li>Provides plenty of storage space for your contacts, music, apps and more. Expand storage up to 200GB by adding a microSD card (sold separately).</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Cloud support lets you access your files anywhere</strong></li><li>Store your photos, videos, documents and other files on Drive for secure access across multiple devices. Fees may apply.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Use your smartphone as a mobile hotspot</strong></li><li>Share your 4G data connection with other compatible wireless devices.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Always on Display</strong></li><li>Get the time or notifications without waking your screen.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Water-resistant IP68</strong></li><li>Repels spills, splashes, and even dunks so you wont be putting all your hopes in a pathetic bowl of rice. Water-resistant in up to 5 feet of water for up to 30 minutes.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 00:37:36', '2016-04-27 00:37:36'),
(24, 'BlackBerry - PRIV 4G with 32GB Memory Cell Phone', 14, 362838028, '649.99', '699.99', 19, 5, 0, '<p><span>his cell phone offers the full ecosystem of Android and its apps to handle all of your business and personal needs. Added security lets you know when your data could be at risk, so you can take action to improve it.</span></p>', '<ul><li>Dual-core 1.8GHz and quad-core 1.44GHz processors with 3GB of RAM</li><li>Deliver outstanding overall performance for opening and running applications, flipping through menus, running home screens and more.</li><li><br></li><li>Android 5.1.1 Lollipop OS</li><li>New colors and typography, new ways to control how you receive messages, and new security features, including Android Smart Lock, which secures your phone by pairing it with a trusted smartwatch or other device.</li><li><br></li><li>4G LTE speed</li><li>Provides fast Web connection for downloading apps, streaming content and staying connected with social media.</li><li><br></li><li>5.4\" dual-curved capacitive touch screen</li><li>Extra-large screen is matched with a slim body to comfortably fit in your hand.</li><li><br></li><li>18.0MP dual-flash Schneider-Kreuznach certified rear-facing camera for HD pictures and videos</li><li>Snap clear and bright photos, even in low-light. The 2.0MP front-facing camera lets you take selfies and videos.</li><li><br></li><li>32GB internal memory plus microSD slot</li><li>Provides plenty of storage space for your contacts, music, apps and more. Expand storage up to 2TB by adding a microSD card (sold separately).</li><li><br></li><li>Use your smartphone as a mobile hotspot</li><li>Share your 4G data connection with other compatible wireless devices.¹</li><li><br></li><li>Slide-out QWERTY keyboard</li><li>Simplifies text messaging and typing. Wide, separated keys help prevent typos.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 00:40:09', '2016-04-27 00:40:09'),
(25, 'Canon - EOS Rebel T5 DSLR Camera with 18-55mm and 75-300mm Lenses', 44, 442680854, '499.99', '749.99', 20, 6, 1, '<p><span>Capture vivid photos and videos with this Canon EOS Rebel T5 DSLR camera that features 18.0-megapixel CMOS sensor that captures up to 5184 x 3456 resolution for high-quality images. The wide array of shooting modes let you optimize your shots to suit your needs.</span></p><p><br></p>', '<ul><li><strong>18.0-megapixel APS-C CMOS sensor</strong></li><li>Captures high-resolution images up to 5184 x 3456 pixels.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>EF-S 18-55mm f/3.5-5.6 IS and EF 75-300mm f/4-5.6 III lenses included</strong></li><li>To enable shooting in a wide variety of situations.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>3\" TFT-LCD monitor</strong></li><li>Provides a clear view of your shots.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>EOS full high-definition movie mode</strong></li><li>Helps you capture quality videos.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>3 fps (frames per second)</strong></li><li>For continuous shooting.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>ISO 100-6400 (expandable to 12,800)</strong></li><li>For shooting in most lighting conditions.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>9-point AF system</strong></li><li>Including 1 center cross-type AF point and AI Servo AF, helps ensure fast autofocus performance and accuracy.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Viewfinder</strong></li><li>Lets you quickly and easily frame your shots.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Built-in flash</strong></li><li>Enables you to take pictures in a variety of conditions.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>Canon DIGIC 4 imaging processor</strong></li><li>Provides fast, high-quality processing.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>Wide selection of shooting modes</strong></li><li>Includes program AE, shutter-priority AE, aperture-priority AE, manual exposure, Scene Intelligent Auto, flash off, creative auto, portrait, landscape, close-up, sports and more.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>Scene Intelligent Auto mode</strong></li><li>Optimizes settings and improves results when shooting at night.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Media slot</strong></li><li>Supports SD, SDHC and SDXC cards.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 03:49:28', '2016-04-27 03:49:28'),
(26, 'Nikon - D5300 DSLR Camera with 18-55mm VR Lens - Black', 22, 428753186, '599.99', '799.99', 20, 14, 0, '<p><strong>Nikon D5300 DSLR Camera with 18–55mm VR lens:</strong><span><span>&nbsp;</span>Achieve crystal-clear shots and high-definition movie footage using the D5300, which comes with a 18–55mm lens that uses VR (Vibration Reduction) image stabilization to limit the effects of camera shake and vibration. Built-in Wi-Fi lets you wireless connect to compatible mobile devices, so you can easily share captured footage with friends, relatives, clients and more.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span>Memory card sold separately.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>EF-S 18–55mm f/3.5–5.6 zoom lens provides versatility</strong></li><li>Creates intricate picture detail.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>18.0-megapixel APS-C CMOS sensor delivers vividly detailed images</strong></li><li>Captures vibrant high-resolution images up to 5184 x 3456 pixels.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>100–12,800 ISO range (expandable to 25,600) for crisp, clear photos even in low light</strong></li><li>Shoot confidently without sacrificing detail, even in extremely low light.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>Capture fast-action shots at up to 5 fps (frames per second)</strong></li><li>This burst mode is not only fast, but also utilizes 9 focus points to keep images sharp even in challenging high-speed shooting situations.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>3\" Vari-angle LCD touch screen provides clear viewing and playback</strong></li><li>Approximately 1,040,000 dots and a smudge-resistant coating for easy navigation and a clear view, even when outdoors.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Capture spectacular movies in HD</strong></li><li>Movie Servo AF, a built-in stereo microphone and Video Snapshot with editing capabilities let you capture detailed video clips.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>DIGIC 5 image processor promotes optimal image capture</strong></li><li>Enjoy rapid performance without sacrificing quality.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Optical viewfinder helps you frame your shots</strong></li><li>Features 95% coverage and approximately 0.85x magnification.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>Face-detection technology puts everybody in their best light</strong></li><li>Detects faces and other subjects to keep them in sharp focus.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Selectable scene modes determine optimal settings</strong></li><li>Include program AE (Scene Intelligent Auto, creative auto, landscape, close-up, sports, special scene modes (night portrait, HDR backlight control) and program), shutter-priority AE and more.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>White balance controls deliver accurate, natural tones, regardless of lighting conditions</strong></li><li>Settings include auto, preset (daylight, shade, cloudy, tungsten light, white fluorescent light, flash), custom and bracketing.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>Built-in flash features multiple modes for optimal lighting conditions</strong></li><li>Choose from flash-ready, flash-exposure compensation, high-speed sync and red-eye reduction.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Multiformat memory card slot for storing or transferring data</strong></li><li>Supports SD, SDHC and SDXC formats. Memory cards not included.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 03:51:19', '2016-04-27 03:52:13'),
(27, 'Sony - Alpha a5000 Mirrorless Camera with 16-50mm Retractable Lens ', 24, 859875737, '399.99', '459.99', 21, 17, 0, '<p><strong>Sony Alpha a5000 Mirrorless Camera with 16–50mm Retractable Lens:</strong><span>You can improve your photo portfolio and preserve memories, all with a single camera. The Sony Alpha a5000 features a 20.1-megapixel Exmor HD CMOS sensor that enables you to document moments in realistic detail. The included 16–50mm lens features a compact design, so it\'s easy to take on the go.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>Sony 16–50mm (35mm equivalent 24–75mm) E-mount lens included</strong></li><li>Get started with a lightweight, ultracompact lens.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>20.1-megapixel APS-C Exmor HD CMOS sensor delivers vividly detailed images</strong></li><li>Capture high-resolution images up to 5456 x 3632 pixels.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>ISO 100–16,000</strong></li><li>Enjoy crisp, clean images over a broad spectrum of lighting conditions, even low-light environments.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Capture fast-action shots at up to 4 fps (frames per second)</strong></li><li>From joyous facial expressions to fast-paced sports action, burst mode ensures you get the shot even if it only lasts a fraction of a second.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>3\" LCD makes it easy to set up and review shots</strong></li><li>Tilts up to 180°, so you can easily take self portraits.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Capture spectacular movies in HD</strong></li><li>High-definition movie mode allows you to record stunningly clear, smooth video clips in up to 1080/60i/24p resolution.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>BIONZ X processing engine delivers speed and performance</strong></li><li>Accelerates autofocus capability, making it easy to rapidly home in on subjects.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Contrast-detect autofocus brings subjects into clear view</strong></li><li>Features 25 focus points to ensure sharp detail.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Wi-Fi connectivity facilitates file sharing</strong></li><li>Wirelessly pair with select cell phones via NFC (near-field communication) technology for simple image transfer.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Built-in pop-up flash for proper illumination</strong></li><li>Brighten scenes, so you can take well-lit pictures.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Multiformat memory slot for storing or transferring data</strong></li><li>Supports SD, SDHC, SDXC and MS PRO Duo formats. Memory cards not included.</li><li><br></li></ul><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 03:55:22', '2016-04-27 03:55:22'),
(28, 'Canon - PowerShot ELPH 350 HS 20.2-Megapixel Digital Camera', 19, 419050990, '159.99', '209.99', 22, 6, 0, '<p><span>This Canon PowerShot ELPH 350 HS digital camera features a 20.2-megapixel CMOS sensor and optical image stabilization, so you can capture clear photos and video footage. Built-in Wi-Fi lets you share stored files across wireless devices.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span>Memory card sold separately.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>20.2-megapixel high-sensitivity CMOS sensor</strong></li><li>Captures high-resolution images up to 5183 x 3888 pixels.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>12x optical/4x digital/48x total zoom</strong></li><li>Through an f/3.6-7 lens for precise zooming and accuracy.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>3\" LCD</strong></li><li>Makes it easy to set up and review shots.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Movie button</strong></li><li>Allows you to record MPEG-4 AVC/H.264 video footage with MPEG-4 AAC-LC stereo sound.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Optical image stabilization</strong></li><li>Reduces the effects of camera shake and vibration to minimize blurring.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Shooting modes</strong></li><li>Include P, hybrid auto, auto, portrait, smart shutter (smile, wink self-timer, face self-timer), high-speed burst, handheld night scene, low light, snow, fireworks and long shutter for versatility.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Autofocus</strong></li><li>Helps you bring subjects and scenes into clear view.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Built-in Wi-Fi</strong></li><li>Makes it easy to share stored files across devices. NFC (near-field communication) technology simplifies pairing with select devices.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Card slot</strong></li><li>Accepts SD, SDHC and SDXC formats.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 03:57:40', '2016-04-27 03:57:40'),
(29, 'GoPro - HERO4 Black 4K Action Camera', 52, 241087568, '499.99', '0.00', 23, 8, 1, '<p><span>Capture the world around you in stunning 4K resolution and super slow motion at up to 240 frames per second with the GoPro 4. GoPro\'s standard waterproof housing lets you record underwater down to 131\', plus built in Wi-Fi and Bluetooth allow you to easily connect to the GoPro App and Smart Remote for simple control and video sharing.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>Capture high-quality 4K video</strong></li><li>With resolutions of 4K30, 2.7K60, 1440p80, 1080p120, 960p120 and 720p240 for ultrasharp, clear footage.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Ultrawide-angle glass lens captures an expansive field of view</strong></li><li>For stunning videos and photos. Ultrawide, medium and narrow field-of-view options allow you to select your perspective.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Capture low-light scenes using Night Photo and Night Lapse modes</strong></li><li>Customize exposure settings for single and time lapse photos. Auto low-light mode adjusts frame rates based on lighting conditions for optimal low-light performance.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Capture stunning 12.0MP photos and burst photos up to 30 fp</strong>s</li><li>Take high-resolution photographs suitable for cropping and enlarging, or hold the shutter button down for burst shooting up to 30 frames per second (fps).</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Turn your camera on and begin recording with the touch of a single button</strong></li><li>QuikCapture one-touch activation ensures you get the shot even when things happen fast.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Built-in Wi-Fi and Bluetooth make it easy to edit, watch and share</strong></li><li>Use the GoPro app (download required) or Smart Remote (sold separately) to wirelessly transfer, watch and edit photos or video, and share them online.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Protune delivers cinema-quality video</strong></li><li>Features manual settings for frame rate, color, ISO limit, exposure and other settings for more dynamic photos and videos.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Create a time-lapse video automatically</strong></li><li>Time-lapse mode lets you select from various time intervals without the need to edit.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Tag key moments for easy reference while recording or playing back videos</strong></li><li>Use the HiLight Tag function on the Smart Remote or GoPro app to zip right to the spot you want to watch or edit.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Standard waterproof housing</strong></li><li>Waterproof down to 131\' when enclosed in housing.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Wearable, mountable design lets you catch all the action from the first-person perspective</strong></li><li>Record the action as it happens — hiking, biking, skiing and more. Compatible with most GoPro mounts. Curved and flat adhesive mounts included.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Record crisp, clear audio</strong></li><li>Built-in microphone records with minimal distortion and a high dynamic range.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>microSD memory card slot</strong></li><li>Supports select memory cards for expansive storage capabilities (memory card not included).</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:02:38', '2016-04-27 04:02:38'),
(30, 'GoPro - HERO4 Silver Action Camera', 50, 625275974, '399.99', '0.00', 23, 8, 0, '<p><span>Capture footage of your adventures in stunning 4K video with the GoPro 4. GoPro\'s wearable, mountable design with touch-screen controls makes it easy to capture the action from your unique first-person perspective. Plus built-in Wi-Fi and Bluetooth allow you to operate the camera controls and share your videos and still shots.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>Capture high-quality 4K video</strong></li><li>With resolutions of 4K15, 2.7K30, 1440p48, 1080p60, 960p100 and 720p120 for ultrasharp, clear footage.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Easily preview shots and control your camera</strong></li><li>The LCD touch-screen display lets you frame the scene before you shoot. Tap and swipe the screen to control the camera and play back content.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Ultrawide-angle glass lens captures an expansive field of view</strong></li><li>For stunning videos and photos. Ultrawide, medium and narrow field-of-view options allow you to select your perspective.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Capture low-light scenes using Night Photo and Night Lapse modes</strong></li><li>Customize exposure settings for single and time lapse photos. Auto low-light mode adjusts frame rates based on lighting conditions for optimal low-light performance.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Capture stunning 12.0MP photos and burst photos up to 30 fps</strong></li><li>Take high-resolution photographs suitable for cropping and enlarging, or hold the shutter button down for burst shooting up to 30 frames per second (fps).</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Built-in Wi-Fi and Bluetooth make it easy to edit, watch and share</strong></li><li>Use the GoPro app (download required) or Smart Remote (sold separately) to wirelessly transfer, watch and edit photos or video, and share them online.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Protune delivers cinema-quality video</strong></li><li>Features manual settings for frame rate, color, ISO limit, exposure and other settings for more dynamic photos and videos.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Create a time-lapse video automatically</strong></li><li>Time-lapse mode lets you select from various time intervals without the need to edit.</li><li><br></li><li>Tag key moments for easy reference while recording or playing back videos</li><li><strong><strong>Use the HiLight Tag function on the Smart Remote or GoPro app (download required) to zip right to the spot you want to watch or edit.</strong></strong></li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Standard waterproof housin</strong>g</li><li>Waterproof down to 131\' when enclosed in housing.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Wearable, mountable design lets you catch all the action from the first-person perspective</strong></li><li>Record the action as it happens — hiking, biking, skiing and more. Compatible with most GoPro mounts. Curved and flat adhesive mounts included.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Record crisp, clear audio</strong></li><li>Built-in microphone records with minimal distortion and a high dynamic range.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>microSD memory card slot</strong></li><li>Supports select memory cards for expansive storage capabilities (memory card not included).</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:06:00', '2016-04-27 04:06:00'),
(31, 'GoPro - HERO4 Session HD Waterproof Action Camera', 74, 804878051, '199.99', '0.00', 23, 8, 1, '<p><strong>GoPro HERO4 Session HD Waterproof Action Camera:</strong><span><span>&nbsp;</span>Capture high-definition footage of your adventures with the GoPro HERO4 Session HD. This waterproof camera has a wearable, mountable design that makes it easy to capture all the action from your unique first-person perspective. Plus built-in Wi-Fi and Bluetooth allow you to operate the camera controls and share your videos and still shots.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>Capture high-quality video</strong></li><li>With resolutions of 1440p30, 1080p60 and 720p100 for crisp, clear footage.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Auto Low Light mode adjusts frame rates based on lighting conditions</strong></li><li>For optimal low-light performance.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Waterproof design</strong></li><li>Lets you capture your underwater adventures in stunning high definition at depths of up to 33\'.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Auto image rotation keeps things right side up</strong></li><li>Automatically adjusts the capture orientation so you don\'t have to adjust it in post-production.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Capture 8.0MP photos and burst photos up to 10 fps</strong></li><li>Take sharp 8.0-megapixel still photographs suitable for cropping and enlarging, or hold the shutter button down for burst shooting up to 10 frames per second (fps).</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Turn your camera on and begin recording with the touch of a single button</strong></li><li>QuikCapture one-touch activation ensures you get the shot even when things happen fast.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Built-in Wi-Fi and Bluetooth make it easy to edit, watch and share</strong></li><li>Use the GoPro app (download required) or Smart Remote (sold separately) to wirelessly transfer, watch and edit photos or video, and share them online.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Protune delivers cinema-quality video</strong></li><li>Features manual settings for ISO limit and sharpness for more dynamic photos and videos.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Tag key moments for easy reference while recording or playing back videos</strong></li><li>Use the HiLight Tag function on the Smart Remote or GoPro app to zip right to the spot you want to watch or edit.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Wearable, mountable design lets you catch all the action from the first-person perspective</strong></li><li>Record the action as it happens — hiking, biking, skiing and more. Compatible with most GoPro mounts. Curved and flat adhesive mounts included.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Dual microphone system</strong></li><li>Automatically switches to the mic that will capture the best audio for reduced wind noise.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>microSD memory card slot</strong></li><li>Supports select memory cards for expansive storage capabilities (memory card not included).</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:08:52', '2016-04-27 04:08:52'),
(32, 'Turtle Beach - Ear Force XO SEVEN PRO Gaming Headset for Xbox One', 62, 211233343, '106.99', '149.99', 25, 19, 1, '<p><span>Dive into your games, chats, movies and music with this headset that features the new Ear Force Headset Audio Controller Plus to deliver customized and optimal sound for your favorite entertainment. Keep close tabs on enemy soldiers or weapon reloads with the help of Superhuman Hearing mode. Plus, the tournament-grade design delivers rugged durability you need for heated competition, as well as amazing audio quality and features needed to win.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>Connect to current gaming devices</strong></li><li>Compatible with your Xbox One, mobile devices and tablets.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Customize the look of your headset</strong></li><li>Customize your headset with dozens of changeable speaker plates (sold separately) depicting everything from your favorite video games to super heroes.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Make your voice heard</strong></li><li>The removable mic boom lets you chat with friends on Xbox Live or Skype, trash-talk opponents and strategize with teammates. Hear your own voice in the headset to avoid shouting with Mic Monitoring.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Booming highs and lows</strong></li><li>Enjoy crisp, clear sound from your video games with the 50mm neodymium speakers.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Lose yourself in your games, movies and music</strong></li><li>The all-new Ear Force Headset Audio Controller Plus lets you customize your audio with innovative tools, such as Superhuman Hearing mode, game and mic presets and Mic Monitoring.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Get the perfect audio balance</strong></li><li>Adjust game and chat volume separately, fine tune the master volume and even mute the microphone.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Enjoy a personalized audio experience</strong></li><li>With game presets, such as Natural Sound, Bass Boost, Bass and Treble Booster and Vocal Booster, and environmental mic presets, like Quiet, Normal and Loud rooms, you can customize your audio.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Pinpoint enemy footsteps and weapon reloads</strong></li><li>Superhuman Hearing mode gives you a competitive advantage on the virtual battlefield.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Stay comfortable</strong></li><li>Play for extended periods with memory foam ear cushions.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Take on your next contest with confidence</strong></li><li>The headset is tournament-ready thanks to its rugged design that withstands heated competition.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:14:17', '2016-04-27 04:14:17'),
(33, 'Microsoft - Xbox One Chat Headset - Black', 93, 881485573, '24.99', '0.00', 25, 13, 1, '<p><span>Keep your in-game communications crisp with the Xbox One Chat Headset. Hear friends and foes in crystal-clear digital audio. The Chat Headset is designed for comfort during long gaming sessions. Plus, you can adjust the mute and volume settings without taking your hands off the controller.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>A better multiplayer experience</strong></li><li>Chat privately with your friends while gaming. Chat in crystal-clear digital audio. Lightweight and comfortable for long gaming sessions. Responsive microphone.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Easy to use</strong></li><li>Connects to Xbox One Wireless Controller—no batteries needed. Mute and volume controls at your fingertips.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Additional features</strong></li><li>On-ear speaker design. Unidirectional microphone. Wearable on left or right ear. Simple to use—plug into controller and go. Can be used for Skype.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:17:17', '2016-04-27 04:17:17'),
(34, 'Astro Gaming - A40 Wired Stereo Gaming Headset for Xbox One', 49, 427691087, '199.99', '219.99', 25, 21, 0, '<p><span>Every detail matters when you\'re gaming. Missing the quiet footsteps of an approaching foe or a crucial command in the heat of battle can mean the difference between an amazing victory and crushing defeat. You want to capture every word of dialogue, each in-game sound and every note of the soundtracks that accompany your favorite games. Surround yourself with high-quality sound with this<span>&nbsp;</span></span><strong>headset</strong><span>.</span></p><p><br></p><p><span>Enjoy every detail of your favorite games\' lush soundscapes with this<span>&nbsp;</span></span><strong>A40 Wired Gaming Headset</strong><span>, which delivers clear, vibrant audio when connected to your Xbox One. Hear even the most subtle sounds in crisp detail with pure, vivid sonic performance. Communicate clearly with fellow players with the included microphone. Stay comfortable during all-day gaming sessions with a lightweight design.</span></p>', '<ul><li>Enhance your audio experience while gaming with this A40 wired headset, A40 microphone, MixAmp, ASTRO speaker tags, 3.3\' A40 audio cable and 1.6\' micro USB cable</li><li><br></li><li>Experience rich, brilliant sound with intense clarity and minute detail</li><li><br></li><li>Communicate clearly with the included microphone</li><li><br></li><li>Stay comfortable during the longest gaming sessions thanks to a lightweight design</li><li><br></li><li>Compatible with Xbox One</li><li><br></li></ul><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:19:21', '2016-04-27 04:19:21'),
(35, 'Turtle Beach - Star Wars X-Wing Pilot Over-The-Ear Gaming Headset', 39, 849391428, '49.99', '0.00', 26, 19, 0, '<p><span>Battle to the top against your gaming enemies and strategize with allies using this Turtle Beach<span>&nbsp;</span></span><strong>Star Wars</strong><span><span>&nbsp;</span>X-Wing Pilot TBS-431001 headset, which is compatible with PlayStation 4, PlayStation Vita, Xbox One, Mac and PC to suit your gaming preferences.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>Over-the-ear design</strong></li><li>Offers comfortable listening during marathon gaming sessions.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>40mm neodymium speakers</strong></li><li>Produce stereo sound with booming lows and clear highs.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Compatible with PlayStation 4, PlayStation Vita, Xbox One, Mac and PC</strong></li><li>For versatile use with your favorite gaming platforms and compatible mobile devices.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>In-line remote</strong></li><li>Provides volume and mute controls at your fingertips, so you can make adjustments while staying focused on the game.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Omnidirectional high-sensitivity microphone with removable boom</strong></li><li>Transmits clear audio, so you can create strategies and triumph over your enemies.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Goes beyond the game</strong></li><li>Utilize the headset for Skype, listening to music and watching videos.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Lightweight construction</strong></li><li>Offers hours of comfort.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Star Wars X-Wing Pilot design</strong></li><li>Helps you channel the Force and defeat the Empire.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:21:26', '2016-04-27 04:21:26'),
(36, 'Sony - Gold Wireless Stereo Headset for PlayStation 4', 72, 738279929, '99.99', '0.00', 26, 17, 1, '<ul><li><br><strong>Product Features</strong></li><li>Connect to most current gaming devices</li><li>Compatible with your PS4, PS3, PlayStation Vita, mobile device, Mac and PC.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Virtual surround sound gaming</strong></li><li>Pinpoint where the action is with the stunning 7.1 virtual surround sound.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Download exclusive audio enhancements</strong></li><li>The Headset Companion app provides custom audio settings created exclusively for PlayStation to enhance audio in supported games.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Make your voice heard</strong></li><li>Reduce unwanted noise with the hidden, noise-canceling microphone.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>Customize the look of your headset</strong></li><li>Removable faceplates (sold separately) can be swapped out to show off your style.</li><li><br></li><li>Full feature set only available on PS4 and PS4 systems. Compatible with most mobile device. Certain features may vary based on device.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '', '2016-04-27 04:22:51', '2016-04-27 04:22:51'),
(37, 'Astro Gaming - A40 Wired Surround Sound Gaming Headset + MIXAMP Pro', 14, 882511634, '249.99', '0.00', 26, 21, 0, '<p><span>You game with the best, so it\'s crucial that you\'re always aware of the environment around you. Every snap of a twig or communication among teammates is critical to getting the win. With the<span>&nbsp;</span></span><strong>A40 Wired Surround Sound Gaming Headset</strong><span>, you can hear every detail in stunning clarity thanks to ASTRO Audio and an optimal balance between in-game sounds and vocal transmissions. It\'s easy to deliver instructions or just chat after a legendary victory with a precision microphone — and when you\'re done playing, simply remove the mic to enjoy your favorite tunes or movie audio. Pro gamers and livestreamers will appreciate the digital components of the included<span>&nbsp;</span></span><strong>MIXAMP Pro</strong><span>, which help make lag and interference a thing of the past. Enhance your next gaming session with bold, crisp sound that puts you in the heart of the action.</span></p>', '<ul><li>Includes A40 Wired Surround Sound Gaming Headset, MIXAMP Pro, ASTRO Command Center software and cables</li><li><br></li><li>Immerse yourself in rich, lifelike sound thanks to ASTRO Audio</li><li><br></li><li>Stay in constant communication during critical missions with a precision microphone that clearly captures vocal sound and can be removed for flexible use</li><li><br></li><li>Make sure you can hear subtle audio details and important conversations with balanced game and voice audio</li><li><br></li><li><strong>MIXAMP Pro</strong></li><li>utilizes reliable all-digital components to prevent lag and interference, so you can live stream your gaming sessions or compete in pro-level tournaments</li><li><br></li><li>Modify your headset to suit your preferences with a variety of optional components, including speaker tags, microphones and ear cushions (not included).</li><li><br></li><li>Compatible with PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3 and Windows</li><li><br></li></ul><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:24:15', '2016-04-27 04:24:15'),
(38, 'Beats by Dr. Dre - Solo 2 On-Ear Headphones - Black', 50, 172362782, '129.99', '199.99', 27, 3, 1, '<p><span>These Beats by Dr. Dre Solo 2 900-00134-01 on-ear headphones feature a compact, foldable design for easy portability. The included RemoteTalk cable lets you take calls and control music with most iOS devices.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>On-ear design</strong></li><li>With leather ear cushions provides comfortable listening.</li><li><strong><br></strong></li><li><strong>RemoteTalk cable with microphone</strong></li><li>Enables you to take calls and control music with most iOS devices.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Compact, foldable design</strong></li><li>Allows easy portability and storage.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Streamlined, lightweight construction</strong></li><li>For extended use.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:29:18', '2016-04-27 04:29:18'),
(39, 'Beats by Dr. Dre - Solo 2 On-Ear Headphones - Red', 54, 927798972, '129.99', '199.99', 27, 3, 0, '<p><span>These Beats by Dr. Dre Solo 2 900-00136-01 on-ear headphones feature a compact, foldable design for easy portability. The included RemoteTalk cable lets you take calls and control music with most iOS devices.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>On-ear design</strong></li><li>With leather ear cushions provides comfortable listening.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>RemoteTalk cable with microphon</strong>e</li><li>Enables you to take calls and control music with most iOS devices.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Compact, foldable design</strong></li><li>Allows easy portability and storage.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Streamlined, lightweight construction</strong></li><li>For extended use.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:31:53', '2016-04-27 04:31:53'),
(40, 'Beats by Dr. Dre - Powerbeats2 Wireless Earbud Headphones - Yellow', 74, 779078901, '149.99', '0.00', 27, 3, 1, '<p><span>The Active Collection\'s Powerbeats2 Wireless earphones give you the freedom to take your run or workout anywhere in style with your iPhone or iPod. Inspired by LeBron James, Beats Powerbeats2 Wireless is designed to defy the ordinary while catapulting athletes towards unparalleled performance. Lightweight and engineered with the power of dual-driver acoustics, the reimagined wireless earphones deliver the premium sound and performance needed to propel you through your run or workout.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong>More freedom. More power.</strong></p><p><span>From the street to the court, Powerbeats2 Wireless gives you the freedom to take your workout anywhere. Wireless Bluetooth gives you the ability to connect up to 30 feet to your iPhone, iPod, or other Bluetooth enabled device—allowing you to move freely and stay focused. A rechargeable battery gives you the power to endure to the end. If you\'re on empty, a quick charge delivers extra non-stop playback.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Built to endure</strong></p><p><span>Don\'t let sweat stop you. Powerbeats2 Wireless is sweat and water resistant, with over-molding on the RemoteTalk control for a no-slip grip when changing volume, switching tracks, and making hands-free calls.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Music you can feel</strong></p><p><span>Add power to your sound. Dual-driver acoustics deliver a wide range of frequency with crisp highs and powerful lows to inspire you through your run and workout.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Designed to perform</strong></p><p><span>We designed it with you, the athlete and runner, in mind. Powerbeats2 Wireless is lightweight and compact with adjustable earhooks, providing a comfortable and secure fit.</span></p>', '<ul><li>Rechargeable battery</li><li><br></li><li>Pair and play with your iPhone, iPad® or other Bluetooth device within a 30-foot range</li><li><br></li><li>Premium sound in a lightweight design with adjustable earhooks</li><li><br></li><li>Sweat and water resistant</li><li><br></li><li>Take hands-free calls and adjust music with no-slip-grip RemoteTalk control*</li><li><br></li><li>Compatible with Apple iPhone 3Gs, 4, 4S, 5, 5c, 5s, 6 and 6 Plus, iPad, iPad 2, iPad 3rd generation, iPad with Retina, iPad mini, iPad mini 2, iPad mini 3, iPad Air and iPad Air 2</li><li><br></li><li>Also compatible with iPod nano 7th generation, iPod touch 2nd-, 3rd- and 4th-generation, 16GB, 32GB and 64GB iPod touch 5th generation, Apple Watch™ 38mm and Apple Watch 42mm</li><li><br></li><li>*Functionality varies by iOS device.</li><li><br></li><li>Apple, the Apple logo and iTunes are trademarks of Apple Computer, Inc., registered in the U.S. and other countries. iPod is a trademark of Apple Computer, Inc.</li><li><br></li><li>iPad is a trademark of Apple Inc., registered in the U.S. and other countries</li><li><br></li><li>Apple Watch™ is a trademark of Apple Inc.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 04:34:15', '2016-04-27 04:34:15'),
(41, 'Bose - QuietComfort 25 Acoustic Noise Cancelling Headphones', 44, 545281504, '299.99', '0.00', 27, 4, 0, '<p><span>Enjoy crisp, powerful sound — and quiet that lets you hear your music better — with these Bose® QuietComfort® 25 around-the-ear headphones, which monitor the noise around you and cancel it out, helping you focus on what matters.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>Bose® noise cancelling technology</strong></li><li>Blocks out the sounds you don\'t want to hear, so you can focus on the music you love.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Proprietary audio technologies</strong></li><li>Bose® Active EQ and TriPort® technologies deliver crisp, clear, full-range sound with deep lows and soaring highs.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Unpowered audio</strong></li><li>Offers performance similar to Bose around-ear audio headphones when the battery runs out.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Around-the-ear design</strong></li><li>With QuietComfort® earcup cushions for optimal performance, reduced ambient noise and comfort during extended listening sessions. Folding earcups provide compact storage for simple transport.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Lightweight materials</strong></li><li>Combined with around-ear fit so comfortable, you can wear them all day long.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>In-line microphone and remote</strong></li><li>Designed for select Apple® iPhone®, iPad® and iPod® models and compatible with other popular phones, so you can easily make and receive hands-free phone calls and control music playback.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 20:32:57', '2016-04-27 20:32:57'),
(42, 'Microsoft - Xbox One 500GB Gears of War: Ultimate Edition Bundle', 74, 561899254, '299.99', '349.99', 28, 13, 0, '<p><span>Featuring a full-game download of Gears of War: Ultimate Edition, the Superstar Cole multiplayer skin, and early access to the Gears of War 4 Beta. Experience the original Gears of War rebuilt from the ground up in 1080p, including 60FPS competitive multiplayer with 19 maps and six game modes, and five campaign chapters never released on console. And for a limited time, when you play Gears of War: Ultimate Edition on Xbox Live, you’ll get the entire Xbox 360 Gears of War collection to play on Xbox One at no additional cost. Gears of War: Ultimate Edition is also your ticket to the Gears of War 4 Beta. This is the first Gears at its best – a bundle for veterans of the series and newcomers alike.</span></p>', '<ul><li><strong>Gears of War: Ultimate Edition game download* included</strong></li><li>Re-experience the epic and legendary title that helped define the first generation of high-definition gaming, fully remastered in full 1080p at 60 fps.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Powerful processing and impressive graphics</strong></li><li>The Xbox One is the most powerful member of the Xbox family to date, able to deliver bigger worlds and better graphics than the Xbox 360.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Wireless controller included</strong></li><li>The Xbox One controller features more than 40 design improvements over the Xbox 360 controller. From refined ergonomics to improved response time, this is a state-of-the-art piece of gaming technology.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Kinect 2.0 (sold separately) gives you the option to play without a controller</strong></li><li>Wave your arms, kick, jump and more to interact with Kinect-enabled games, and command apps with your voice or a wave of your hand.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>500GB of storage</strong></li><li>Substantial hard drive lets you store several blockbuster games and plenty of apps, indie titles, recorded game footage and more without running out of room.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>A robust catalog of streaming video services</strong></li><li>Your Xbox One acts as an all-in-one media streaming hub with Netflix**, Hulu Plus**, HBO Go** and more. Xbox Video allows you to buy or rent videos digitally.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Stream a multitude of sports in HD</strong></li><li>Sports on Xbox brings several streaming platforms together into one convenient place, with apps such as ESPN,* the NFL on Xbox One and more.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>Watch cable TV without unplugging anything</strong></li><li>HDMI pass-thru lets you keep your cable TV hooked up through your Xbox One, so switching between TV and gaming is quick and easy.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>The Internet comes to your console</strong></li><li>Surf the Internet from the comfort of your couch with Internet Explorer for Xbox One, which works in conjunction with Kinect (sold separately) to let you browse using voice commands.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>3 USB 3.0 ports to connect headsets and peripherals to your Xbox One</strong></li><li>With a Play &amp; Charge kit, controller batteries can be charged via micro USB cable. (Won\'t recharge generic rechargeable batteries. Play &amp; Charge kit sold separately.)</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Connect with your mobile devices</strong></li><li>SmartGlass allows you to interact using your PC, smartphone or tablet. Navigate menus, display additional information about the videos you watch, and use multiplayer matchmaking without interrupting your game.</li><li><br></li><li><strong>Blu-ray delivers exceptional video quality for your games and movies</strong></li><li>Watch Blu-ray and DVD video content. Blu-ray game discs have several times the capacity of DVD-based discs, allowing massive games to fit comfortably on a single disc.</li><li><strong><br></strong><br></li><li><strong>14 days of Xbox Live Gold included</strong></li><li>Xbox Live brings you an elegant online experience, where you can play your games online, set up chat groups, talk with your friends, watch streaming video, and more.</li></ul><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '2016-04-27 20:37:16', '2016-04-27 20:38:28');
